               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-183-cd1037" type="crimeDate">2d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-183-off1036 t18270913-183-cd1037"></join>, 1 hat, value 10s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18270913-183-victim1746" type="victimName">
                  Thomas Green 
                  Phillips
               <interp inst="t18270913-183-victim1746" type="surname" value="Phillips"></interp>
